<plot>Japan, known only decades ago a society of buttoned-down workaholics, has experienced a cultural revolution to match the West's. In this documentary, we come face-to-face with Japan's own Flower Children: music buffs, dancers, costume enthusiasts, amateur artists, and the world's most colorful fashion maniacs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?103194</url></doc>
